{"segment_id": "shangshu-042-zhou-shu-announcement-of-the-duke-of-shao__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3__segment-001", "work_id": "shangshu", "section_id": "shangshu-042-zhou-shu-announcement-of-the-duke-of-shao", "source_id": "shangshu-042-zhou-shu-announcement-of-the-duke-of-shao__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 1, "canonical_ref": "尚書·周書 召誥 [1]", "text_original": "惟二月既望，越六日乙未，王朝步自周，則至于豐。", "text_normalized": "惟二月既望，越六日乙未，王朝步自周，則至于豐。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "shangshu-042-zhou-shu-announcement-of-the-duke-of-shao__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3__segment-002", "work_id": "shangshu", "section_id": "shangshu-042-zhou-shu-announcement-of-the-duke-of-shao", "source_id": "shangshu-042-zhou-shu-announcement-of-the-duke-of-shao__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 2, "canonical_ref": "尚書·周書 召誥 [2]", "text_original": "惟太保先周公相宅；越若來三月，惟丙午朏，越三日戊申，太保朝至于洛，卜宅。厥既得卜，則經營。越三日庚戌，太保乃以庶殷，攻位于洛汭；越五日甲寅，位成。", "text_normalized": "惟太保先周公相宅；越若來三月，惟丙午朏，越三日戊申，太保朝至于洛，卜宅。厥既得卜，則經營。越三日庚戌，太保乃以庶殷，攻位于洛汭；越五日甲寅，位成。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "shangshu-042-zhou-shu-announcement-of-the-duke-of-shao__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3__segment-003", "work_id": "shangshu", "section_id": "shangshu-042-zhou-shu-announcement-of-the-duke-of-shao", "source_id": "shangshu-042-zhou-shu-announcement-of-the-duke-of-shao__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 3, "canonical_ref": "尚書·周書 召誥 [3]", "text_original": "若翼日乙卯，周公朝至于洛，則達觀于新邑營。越三日丁巳，用牲于郊，牛二。越翼日戊午，乃社于新邑，牛一、羊一、豕一。", "text_normalized": "若翼日乙卯，周公朝至于洛，則達觀于新邑營。越三日丁巳，用牲于郊，牛二。越翼日戊午，乃社于新邑，牛一、羊一、豕一。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "shangshu-042-zhou-shu-announcement-of-the-duke-of-shao__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3__segment-004", "work_id": "shangshu", "section_id": "shangshu-042-zhou-shu-announcement-of-the-duke-of-shao", "source_id": "shangshu-042-zhou-shu-announcement-of-the-duke-of-shao__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 4, "canonical_ref": "尚書·周書 召誥 [4]", "text_original": "越七日甲子，周公乃朝用書命庶殷--侯、甸、男、邦伯。厥既命殷庶，庶殷丕作。", "text_normalized": "越七日甲子，周公乃朝用書命庶殷--侯、甸、男、邦伯。厥既命殷庶，庶殷丕作。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "shangshu-042-zhou-shu-announcement-of-the-duke-of-shao__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3__segment-005", "work_id": "shangshu", "section_id": "shangshu-042-zhou-shu-announcement-of-the-duke-of-shao", "source_id": "shangshu-042-zhou-shu-announcement-of-the-duke-of-shao__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 5, "canonical_ref": "尚書·周書 召誥 [5]", "text_original": "太保乃以庶邦冢君，出取幣，乃復入，錫周公。", "text_normalized": "太保乃以庶邦冢君，出取幣，乃復入，錫周公。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "shangshu-042-zhou-shu-announcement-of-the-duke-of-shao__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3__segment-006", "work_id": "shangshu", "section_id": "shangshu-042-zhou-shu-announcement-of-the-duke-of-shao", "source_id": "shangshu-042-zhou-shu-announcement-of-the-duke-of-shao__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 6, "canonical_ref": "尚書·周書 召誥 [6]", "text_original": "曰：「拜手稽首，旅王若公。誥告庶殷，越自乃御事。嗚呼！皇天上帝，改厥元子茲大國殷之命。惟王受命，無疆惟休，亦無疆惟恤。嗚呼！曷其奈何弗敬！", "text_normalized": "曰：「拜手稽首，旅王若公。誥告庶殷，越自乃御事。嗚呼！皇天上帝，改厥元子茲大國殷之命。惟王受命，無疆惟休，亦無疆惟恤。嗚呼！曷其奈何弗敬！", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "shangshu-042-zhou-shu-announcement-of-the-duke-of-shao__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3__segment-007", "work_id": "shangshu", "section_id": "shangshu-042-zhou-shu-announcement-of-the-duke-of-shao", "source_id": "shangshu-042-zhou-shu-announcement-of-the-duke-of-shao__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 7, "canonical_ref": "尚書·周書 召誥 [7]", "text_original": "天既遐終大邦殷之命。茲殷多先哲王在天，越厥後王后民，茲服厥命；厥終智藏瘝在。夫知保抱攜持厥婦子，以哀吁天；徂厥亡出執。」", "text_normalized": "天既遐終大邦殷之命。茲殷多先哲王在天，越厥後王后民，茲服厥命；厥終智藏瘝在。夫知保抱攜持厥婦子，以哀吁天；徂厥亡出執。」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "shangshu-042-zhou-shu-announcement-of-the-duke-of-shao__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3__segment-008", "work_id": "shangshu", "section_id": "shangshu-042-zhou-shu-announcement-of-the-duke-of-shao", "source_id": "shangshu-042-zhou-shu-announcement-of-the-duke-of-shao__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 8, "canonical_ref": "尚書·周書 召誥 [8]", "text_original": "「嗚呼！天亦哀于四方民，其眷命用懋，王其疾敬德。", "text_normalized": "「嗚呼！天亦哀于四方民，其眷命用懋，王其疾敬德。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "shangshu-042-zhou-shu-announcement-of-the-duke-of-shao__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3__segment-009", "work_id": "shangshu", "section_id": "shangshu-042-zhou-shu-announcement-of-the-duke-of-shao", "source_id": "shangshu-042-zhou-shu-announcement-of-the-duke-of-shao__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 9, "canonical_ref": "尚書·周書 召誥 [9]", "text_original": "相古先民有夏，天迪從子保；面稽天若，今時既墜厥命。今相有殷，天迪格保；面稽天若，今時既墜厥命。今沖子嗣，則無遺壽耇；曰：其稽我古人之德，矧曰其有能稽謀自天。", "text_normalized": "相古先民有夏，天迪從子保；面稽天若，今時既墜厥命。今相有殷，天迪格保；面稽天若，今時既墜厥命。今沖子嗣，則無遺壽耇；曰：其稽我古人之德，矧曰其有能稽謀自天。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "shangshu-042-zhou-shu-announcement-of-the-duke-of-shao__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3__segment-010", "work_id": "shangshu", "section_id": "shangshu-042-zhou-shu-announcement-of-the-duke-of-shao", "source_id": "shangshu-042-zhou-shu-announcement-of-the-duke-of-shao__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 10, "canonical_ref": "尚書·周書 召誥 [10]", "text_original": "嗚呼！有王雖小，元子哉。其丕能諴于小民，今休。王不敢後，用顧畏于民碞。王來紹上帝，自服于土中。旦曰：『其作大邑，其自時配皇天；毖祀于上下，其自時中乂，王厥有成命，治民今休。』王先服殷御事，比介于我有周御事。節性，惟日其邁；王敬作所，不可不敬德。」", "text_normalized": "嗚呼！有王雖小，元子哉。其丕能諴于小民，今休。王不敢後，用顧畏于民碞。王來紹上帝，自服于土中。旦曰：『其作大邑，其自時配皇天；毖祀于上下，其自時中乂，王厥有成命，治民今休。』王先服殷御事，比介于我有周御事。節性，惟日其邁；王敬作所，不可不敬德。」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "shangshu-042-zhou-shu-announcement-of-the-duke-of-shao__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3__segment-011", "work_id": "shangshu", "section_id": "shangshu-042-zhou-shu-announcement-of-the-duke-of-shao", "source_id": "shangshu-042-zhou-shu-announcement-of-the-duke-of-shao__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 11, "canonical_ref": "尚書·周書 召誥 [11]", "text_original": "「我不可不監于有夏，亦不可不監于有殷。我不敢知曰，有夏服天命，惟有歷年；我不敢知曰，不其延，惟不敬厥德，乃早墜厥命。我不敢知曰，有殷受天命，惟有歷年；我不敢知曰，不其延，惟不敬厥德，乃早墜厥命。今王嗣受厥命，我亦惟茲二國命，嗣若功。", "text_normalized": "「我不可不監于有夏，亦不可不監于有殷。我不敢知曰，有夏服天命，惟有歷年；我不敢知曰，不其延，惟不敬厥德，乃早墜厥命。我不敢知曰，有殷受天命，惟有歷年；我不敢知曰，不其延，惟不敬厥德，乃早墜厥命。今王嗣受厥命，我亦惟茲二國命，嗣若功。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "shangshu-042-zhou-shu-announcement-of-the-duke-of-shao__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3__segment-012", "work_id": "shangshu", "section_id": "shangshu-042-zhou-shu-announcement-of-the-duke-of-shao", "source_id": "shangshu-042-zhou-shu-announcement-of-the-duke-of-shao__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 12, "canonical_ref": "尚書·周書 召誥 [12]", "text_original": "王乃初服；嗚呼！若生子，罔不在厥初生；自貽哲命。今天其命哲，命吉兇，命歷年。知今我初服，宅新邑，肆惟王其疾敬德。王其德之用，祈天永命。", "text_normalized": "王乃初服；嗚呼！若生子，罔不在厥初生；自貽哲命。今天其命哲，命吉兇，命歷年。知今我初服，宅新邑，肆惟王其疾敬德。王其德之用，祈天永命。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "shangshu-042-zhou-shu-announcement-of-the-duke-of-shao__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3__segment-013", "work_id": "shangshu", "section_id": "shangshu-042-zhou-shu-announcement-of-the-duke-of-shao", "source_id": "shangshu-042-zhou-shu-announcement-of-the-duke-of-shao__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 13, "canonical_ref": "尚書·周書 召誥 [13]", "text_original": "其惟王勿以小民淫用非彝，亦敢殄戮；用乂民，若有功。其惟王位在德元，小民乃惟刑；用于天下，越王顯。上下勤恤，其曰：『我受天命，丕若有夏歷年，式勿替有殷歷年。』欲王以小民受天永命。」", "text_normalized": "其惟王勿以小民淫用非彝，亦敢殄戮；用乂民，若有功。其惟王位在德元，小民乃惟刑；用于天下，越王顯。上下勤恤，其曰：『我受天命，丕若有夏歷年，式勿替有殷歷年。』欲王以小民受天永命。」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "shangshu-042-zhou-shu-announcement-of-the-duke-of-shao__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3__segment-014", "work_id": "shangshu", "section_id": "shangshu-042-zhou-shu-announcement-of-the-duke-of-shao", "source_id": "shangshu-042-zhou-shu-announcement-of-the-duke-of-shao__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 14, "canonical_ref": "尚書·周書 召誥 [14]", "text_original": "拜手稽首曰：「予小臣，敢以王之讎民、百君子、越友民，保受王威命明德。王末有成命，王亦顯。我非敢勤，惟恭奉幣、用供王，能祈天永命。」", "text_normalized": "拜手稽首曰：「予小臣，敢以王之讎民、百君子、越友民，保受王威命明德。王末有成命，王亦顯。我非敢勤，惟恭奉幣、用供王，能祈天永命。」", "notes": ""}
